This is the Webex Contact Center postman collection v3 - updated August 2023.  
Set up the authorization centrally using this tab.

All the APIs will inherit the token once the OAuth2 Flow is complete.

Create the following Environment Variables in the Environment Tab before starting:

`access_token` - {Copy and Paste this after OAuth2 flow completes}

`refresh_token` - {Copy and Paste this after OAuth2 flow completes}

`accessToken_url` - [https://webexapis.com/v1/access_token](https://webexapis.com/v1/access_token)

`grant_type` - {refresh_token}

`client_id` - {Your client ID}

`client_secret` - {Your Client Secret}

`auth_url` - [https://webexapis.com/v1/authorize](https://webexapis.com/v1/authorize)

`scope` - cjp:config cjp:config_read cjp:config_write

`org_id` - {Your org Id}

`startTimer` - This needs to be an epoch timestamp

`expires` - leave this blank, the script will auto-populate this value.

`datacenter` - One of us1,eu1,eu2,anz1 and so on.

